casebody.data:
Eitan LEASCHAUER, petitioner,
v.
NATIONAL TRANSPORTATION SAFETY BOARD, et al. No. 16-6447. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 9, 2017.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner allowed until January 30, 2017, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance *709with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
